{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"區塊級元素","mdn_url":"/zh-TW/docs/Web/HTML/Block-level_elements","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>HTML (超文字標記語言, <strong>Hypertext Markup Language</strong>) 元素通常為 \"區塊級\" 元素或是 <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Inline_elements\">\"行內\" 元素</a>。 一個區塊級元素會藉由建立\"區塊\"的動作, 完全佔滿其父元素(容器)的空間。本文將為您說明其意涵.</p>\n\n<p>瀏覽器預設以在元素前後換行的方式, 表現區塊級元素. 視覺上會呈現為一排縱向堆疊的方塊。</p>\n\n<div class=\"note notecard\" id=\"sect1\">\n<p>區塊級元素必定以換行方式, 取得完整寬度的空間(向左右兩側儘可能地延伸出去)。</p>\n</div>\n\n<p>以下範例將展示區塊級元素的影響:</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"block-level_example","title":"區塊級元素","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"html","title":"HTML","isH3":true,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>This paragraph is a block-level element; its background has been colored to display the paragraph's parent element.<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span></code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"css","title":"CSS","isH3":true,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: css notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token selector\">p</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"token property\">background-color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> #8ABB55<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n\n<p><iframe class=\"sample-code-frame\" title=\"Block-level Example sample\" id=\"frame_block-level_example\" src=\"https://yari-demos.prod.mdn.mozit.cloud/zh-TW/docs/Web/HTML/Block-level_elements/_sample_.block-level_example.html\" loading=\"lazy\"></iframe></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"用法","title":"用法","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li>區塊級元素只能出現於 <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/body\"><code>&lt;body&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> 元素之內.</li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"區塊級_vs._行內元素","title":"區塊級 vs. 行內元素","isH3":false,"content":"<p>There are a couple of key differences between block-level elements and inline elements:</p>\n\n<dl>\n <dt id=\"formatting\">Formatting</dt>\n <dd>By default, block-level elements begin on new lines, but inline elements can start anywhere in a line.</dd>\n <dt id=\"content_model\">Content model</dt>\n <dd>Generally, block-level elements may contain inline elements and other block-level elements. Inherent in this structural distinction is the idea that block elements create \"larger\" structures than inline elements.</dd>\n</dl>\n\n<p>The distinction of block-level vs. inline elements is used in HTML specifications up to 4.01. In HTML5, this binary distinction is replaced with a more complex set of <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Guide/HTML/Content_categories\">content categories</a>. The \"block-level\" category roughly corresponds to the category of <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Guide/HTML/Content_categories#flow_content\">flow content</a> in HTML5, while \"inline\" corresponds to <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Guide/HTML/Content_categories#phrasing_content\">phrasing content</a>, but there are additional categories.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"相關元素","title":"相關元素","isH3":false,"content":"<p>The following is a complete list of all HTML block level elements (although \"block-level\" is not technically defined for elements that are new in HTML5).</p>\n\n<dl>\n <dt id=\"address_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/address\"><code>&lt;address&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>Contact information.</dd>\n <dt id=\"article_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/article\"><code>&lt;article&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>Article content.</dd>\n <dt id=\"aside_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/aside\"><code>&lt;aside&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>Aside content.</dd>\n <dt id=\"blockquote\"><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/HTML/Element/blockquote\"><code>&lt;blockquote&gt;</code></a></dt>\n <dd>Long (\"block\") quotation.</dd>\n <dt id=\"dialog_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/dialog\"><code>&lt;dialog&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>Dialog box.</dd>\n <dt id=\"dd_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/dd\"><code>&lt;dd&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>Describes a term in a description list.</dd>\n <dt id=\"div\"><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/HTML/Element/div\"><code>&lt;div&gt;</code></a></dt>\n <dd>Document division.</dd>\n <dt id=\"dl_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/dl\"><code>&lt;dl&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>Description list.</dd>\n <dt id=\"dt_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/dt\"><code>&lt;dt&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>Description list term.</dd>\n <dt id=\"fieldset_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/fieldset\"><code>&lt;fieldset&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>Field set label.</dd>\n <dt id=\"figcaption_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/figcaption\"><code>&lt;figcaption&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>Figure caption.</dd>\n <dt id=\"figure_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/figure\"><code>&lt;figure&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>Groups media content with a caption (see <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/figcaption\"><code>&lt;figcaption&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>).</dd>\n <dt id=\"footer_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/footer\"><code>&lt;footer&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>Section or page footer.</dd>\n <dt id=\"form\"><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/HTML/Element/form\"><code>&lt;form&gt;</code></a></dt>\n <dd>Input form.</dd>\n <dt id=\"h1_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Heading_Elements\"><code>&lt;h1&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Heading_Elements\"><code>&lt;h2&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Heading_Elements\"><code>&lt;h3&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Heading_Elements\"><code>&lt;h4&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Heading_Elements\"><code>&lt;h5&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Heading_Elements\"><code>&lt;h6&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>Heading levels 1-6.</dd>\n <dt id=\"header_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/header\"><code>&lt;header&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>Section or page header.</dd>\n <dt id=\"hgroup_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/hgroup\"><code>&lt;hgroup&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>Groups header information.</dd>\n <dt id=\"hr\"><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/HTML/Element/hr\"><code>&lt;hr&gt;</code></a></dt>\n <dd>Horizontal rule (dividing line).</dd>\n <dt id=\"li_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/li\"><code>&lt;li&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>List item.</dd>\n <dt id=\"main_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/main\"><code>&lt;main&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>Contains the central content unique to this document.</dd>\n <dt id=\"nav\"><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/HTML/Element/nav\"><code>&lt;nav&gt;</code></a></dt>\n <dd>Contains navigation links.</dd>\n <dt id=\"ol_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/ol\"><code>&lt;ol&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>Ordered list.</dd>\n <dt id=\"p_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/p\"><code>&lt;p&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>Paragraph.</dd>\n <dt id=\"pre_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/pre\"><code>&lt;pre&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>Preformatted text.</dd>\n <dt id=\"section_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/section\"><code>&lt;section&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>Section of a web page.</dd>\n <dt id=\"table\"><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/HTML/Element/table\"><code>&lt;table&gt;</code></a></dt>\n <dd>Table.</dd>\n <dt id=\"ul_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/ul\"><code>&lt;ul&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>Unordered list.</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"see_also","title":"參閱","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Inline_elements\">行內元素</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"區塊級元素","id":"block-level_example"},{"text":"用法","id":"用法"},{"text":"區塊級 vs. 行內元素","id":"區塊級_vs._行內元素"},{"text":"相關元素","id":"相關元素"}],"summary":"HTML (超文字標記語言, Hypertext Markup Language) 元素通常為 \"區塊級\" 元素或是 \"行內\" 元素。 一個區塊級元素會藉由建立\"區塊\"的動作, 完全佔滿其父元素(容器)的空間。本文將為您說明其意涵.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Block-Level Elemente","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch"},{"title":"Block-level elements","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Elementos en bloque","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"Éléments de bloc","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"ブロックレベル要素","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"블록 레벨 요소","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"Elementy blokowe","locale":"pl","native":"Polski"},{"title":"Elementos block-level","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"Блочные элементы","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"块级元素","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-tw/web/html/block-level_elements","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/tr